"Das Altbierlied" (The Altbier song) is a schlager drinking song originally by Hans Ludwig Lonsdorfer. "Das Altbierlied" was covered by Die Toten Hosen for the album Damenwahl, from which it was released as the only single.
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
